{"title":"英语课句型转换","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":62,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2863","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>第二节是英语课，今天作句型转换，汉子老师走了进来……</p>\n<p>将陈述句转换为感叹句是英语的经典题型。因此，汉子老师让我们练习一下，谦哥的英语很差，你能帮帮他吗？<br><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行，一个字符串，What或How，表示感叹句由什么来引导，第二行，一个字符串，表示原句(0＜长度≤2^8)。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一行，表示改后的句子(感叹句)。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>What<br>It is a lovely dog!</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>What a lovely dog it is!</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>提示：string类型范围：(0＜长度＜2^8)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}